org.bennedum.transporter.api

Interface Reservation


  • public interface Reservation
    Represents a reservation to teleport an entity.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Gate getArrivalGate()
      Returns the arrival gate the entity arrived at, or null if the entity didn't arrive at a gate.
      Gate getDepartureGate()
      Returns the departure gate the entity left from, or null if the entity didn't depart from a gate.
      org.bukkit.entity.Entity getEntity()
      Returns the local entity this reservation is for.
